<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>🔥 Самая жёсткая Галерея Мемов 🔥</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', cursive, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #222;
            color: white;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        .gallery {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 10px;
        }
        .meme {
            position: relative;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out;
        }
        .meme:hover {
            transform: scale(1.2) rotate(3deg);
        }
        img {
            max-width: 350px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.8);
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }
        .meme {
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
        }
    </style>
    <script>
        function playSound() {
            let audio = new Audio('poop.mp3');
            audio.play();
        }
        function playWelcomeSound() {
            let welcomeAudio = new Audio('welcome.mp3');
            welcomeAudio.play();
        }
        window.onload = playWelcomeSound;
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>🔥 Самая жёсткая Галерея Мемов 🔥</h1>
    <marquee scrollamount="15">Эй, салага! Добро пожаловать в мир грязных мемов! 🚀</marquee>
    <div class="gallery">
        <div class="meme" onmouseover="playSound()">
            <img src="meme1.png" alt="Мем 1">
        </div>
        <div class="meme" onmouseover="playSound()">
            <img src="meme2.png" alt="Мем 2">
        </div>
        <div class="meme" onmouseover="playSound()">
            <img src="meme3.png" alt="Мем 3">
        </div>
        <div class="meme" onmouseover="playSound()">
            <img src="meme4.png" alt="Мем 4">
        </div>
        <div class="meme" onmouseover="playSound()">
            <img src="meme5.png" alt="Мем 5">
        </div>
        <div class="meme" onmouseover="playSound()">
            <img src="meme6.png" alt="Мем 6">
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
